@EndUserText.label: 'Created Ledgers'
//@Metadata.ignorePropagatedAnnotations: true
define root view entity zetr_ddl_i_created_ledger
  as select from zetr_t_defcl  as Ledger
  composition [1..1] of zetr_ddl_i_created_ledger_tot  as _ledgerTotals
  composition [1..*] of zetr_ddl_i_created_ledger_part as _ledgerParts
{
  key Ledger.bukrs     as bukrs,
  key Ledger.gjahr     as gjahr,
  key Ledger.monat     as monat,
      Ledger.elprc     as elprc,
      Ledger.stldr     as stldr,
      Ledger.etldr     as etldr,
      Ledger.stldd     as stldd,
      Ledger.stsds     as stsds,
      Ledger.etsds     as etsds,
      Ledger.sgbsn     as sgbsn,
      Ledger.egbsn     as egbsn,
      Ledger.dcdrs     as dcdrs,
      Ledger.heror     as heror,
      Ledger.manup     as manup,
      Ledger.ernam     as ernam,
      Ledger.erdat     as erdat,
      Ledger.erzet     as erzet,

      _ledgerTotals,
      _ledgerParts
}
